    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very dependable; the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely without any issues. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of regular use, and the exterior paint still retains a nice luster with only a few small, expected blemishes. Overall, this is a solid, reliable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
