    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and a commanding presence. It exhibits a high degree of mechanical integrity and has been maintained to a standard that ensures continued performance and comfort. With its refined interior and well-preserved exterior, this offering represents a significant value for those seeking a premium pre-owned experience without compromise.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? This car has been my trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape. It runs super smoothly, looks great, and has been really well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine paired with a 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal remains bone dry. The suspension geometry is sharpened by Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, preserving the communicative steering and rear-biased turn-in characteristics these chassis are known for. It retains its factory-applied finish with minor road-going patina, while the interior shows well-preserved bolsters. Recent service includes a low-temperature thermostat and a cooling system flush to ensure optimal thermal management during spirited driving. A mechanically sorted, high-revving flat-six ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership. The exterior retains a deep, consistent luster, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of a well-maintained car that has seen the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and odor-free; the upholstery remains supple with only light creasing, and all electronic components\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, offering a smooth, quiet ride and responsive handling thanks to a consistent service history. It is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between a daily driver and a weekend showpiece.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a superb balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and showing clear evidence of pride in ownership, the automobile features a robust mechanical profile and a highly preserved interior. Every primary system has been evaluated to ensure it meets our exacting standards for reliability and roadworthiness. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a sophisticated, dependable vehicle that performs with precision and command.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me over the years! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs beautifully, and is totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love driving it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 320hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The powerplant utilizes VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve and linear delivery throughout the rev range. The chassis maintains its signature poise with a McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent thermal management and stopping power, this example represents a mechanically robust entry into the analog Porsche experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
